                    	 <span class="main-heading-1"><b>D0140 only Covered with x rays, If performed with other treatment amounts to be collected from patient and WO to insurance at $0.</b></span>
					 </td>
                      <td  colspan="10"></td>
					 
            </tr>
            </table>
			</xsl:if>
            <table>
			<tr>
